"""Smart clamp: detect bimodal tops in each tile, use deep cluster's p10.

For each tile:
- Sort tops by z
- Find largest gap between consecutive z values
- If gap > GAP_TH (e.g., 60µm) AND deep cluster has enough points (>= MIN_DEEP),
  take p10 of the DEEP cluster only; else p10 of all tops.

This should:
- Keep clean subjects intact (unimodal → no change)
- Fix 755252 (AF vs pia are separated, reject AF cluster)
"""
